title: [Updated] Complete Texas Chainsaw Comics Collection [June 2016]
description:
It was brought to my attention that I was missing some comics in my first torrent, mostly Wildstorm one-shots, but this has been rectified.


Torrent Contains:




Jason vs Leatherface [Topps]

Leatherface          [Northstar]

Fearbook             [Avatar]
T
The Grind            [Avatar]

Special              [Avatar]

Americarnivore       [Wildstorm]

Raising Cain         [Wildstorm]

About a boy          [Wildstorm]

By Himself           [Wildstorm]

Cut!                 [Wildstorm]





It's hard to find horror comics on the net, mostly due to the death of file lockers and websites like Magazine3k. I have a few more collections I'm going to upload in the coming weeks: X-files, Cadillacs and Dinosaurs, Mars Attacks, Clive Barker Comics, Stephen King Comics, and many more. I just want to give back to the community while I can so everyone gets a chance to read these
